node.name: squishmatic-project
node.description: The main idea is to create a new system environment to exploit the whole potentiality of augmented reality and mixed reality, which works almost everywhere, cross-platform, reusing existing applications. At his base: virtualization and containers, each application should have a sandbox and reuse the same context when this is possible, to avoid an excessive resources utilization. [] Combining this system environment with an innovative wearable 3D viewer device, light, not bulky and also beautiful to wear, together with home automation components from IoT or a full system for home or office, could be a great strength for its diffusion.
